250
00:19:39,300 --> 00:19:44,230
I think the hardest relationships in the world are ones with your family.

251
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:48,740
You hurt each other the most, yet have the strongest affection for one another.

252
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:50,540
I don't want to be friendly.

253
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:55,580
No one asks you to be friendly. You're placing that pressure on yourself.

254
00:19:55,580 --> 00:19:57,640
Aren't you going to tell me to be friendly?

255
00:19:57,640 --> 00:20:02,710
