256
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:05,300
That's comforting in this situation.

257
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:07,600
How can you be this cool?

258
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:09,780
Oh, my... Cheesy...

259
00:20:09,780 --> 00:20:13,350
I really like that you're my man.

260
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:15,110
Am I your man?

261
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:17,910
Yes. You're my man.

262
00:20:22,170 --> 00:20:27,280
Long time no see. The beagles must not come by anymore, since you don't come by my place anymore.

263
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,440
Yes. I'll be going now.

264
00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:56,930
- Oh my!
- Did I startle you?

265
00:20:56,930 --> 00:20:59,380
I thought you were in the middle of a date. How did you come here?

266
00:20:59,380 --> 00:21:01,470
Hey, do you want to have dinner together?

267
00:21:01,470 --> 00:21:04,590
