- Don't bother.

270
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:12,640
Bring some alcohol if you have some.

271
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:16,820
I said don't bother! Why are you ignoring my opinion...?

272
00:21:24,340 --> 00:21:25,710
