273
00:21:25,710 --> 00:21:29,550
He'll be back shortly. The chief director came by so he stepped out for a moment.

274
00:21:29,550 --> 00:21:31,480
Okay.

275
00:22:07,830 --> 00:22:12,180
I'm going to kill you.

276
00:22:13,470 --> 00:22:16,450
