278
00:22:24,290 --> 00:22:25,940
You're here.

279
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:30,820
What is it?

280
00:22:33,100 --> 00:22:34,600
I heard from Hye Jeong.

281
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:36,940
I don't want to hear her name.

282
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:40,000
It's a medical accident! Who would want to have one?

283
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:43,550
She would know as a doctor but I don't know why she's like that. I'm so tired!

284
00:22:43,550 --> 00:22:45,220
What did she do to you?

285
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:48,940
I don't want to talk about it. I have a headache.

286
00:22:48,940 --> 00:22:50,130
Does it hurt?

287
00:22:50,130 --> 00:22:53,430
I'm stressed out, since I have a lot on my plate.

288
00:22:58,450 --> 00:22:59,790
Are you leaving?

289
00:22:59,790 --> 00:23:01,830
I need to look into something.

290
00:23:09,450 --> 00:23:11,830
I looked into it after speaking with you, Director.

291
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:16,580
Regarding my grandma... I found a way to make it a legal issue.

292
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:19,830
- You found it?
- There was none.

293
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:22,460
So, I found another way.

294
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:26,680
I will kill you.

295
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:41,320
Operating Room

