318
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,910
Why?

319
00:25:10,910 --> 00:25:15,640
Due to your kindness toward me, I did very well on that math exam.

320
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:18,550
And that became the trigger for me in knowing how to study.

321
00:25:19,670 --> 00:25:22,640
You gave me a lot of things in life with that.

322
00:25:24,280 --> 00:25:26,320
That's why I held it in.

323
00:25:51,360 --> 00:25:54,970
I'm suspicious. Looks like something happened.

324
00:25:54,970 --> 00:26:00,090
Something did. I got to go to the DBS Research Center as Center Chief.

325
00:26:00,090 --> 00:26:01,600
Does it change anything?

326
00:26:01,600 --> 00:26:06,580
Do you know the feeling? Hating something really badly, but really wanting to do it.

327
00:26:16,630 --> 00:26:19,380
- Welcome.
- Yeah.

328
00:26:19,380 --> 00:26:21,670
I made steaks, but I cooked it the way I want to.

329
00:26:21,670 --> 00:26:25,050
I'll eat whatever you serve. Here, alcohol.

330
00:26:25,050 --> 00:26:28,220
Vintage wine. It's expensive.

331
00:26:34,610 --> 00:26:36,190
Here.

332
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:43,920
