333
00:26:46,210 --> 00:26:49,680
I couldn't even say thank you all this time.

334
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:55,090
When my father passed away and also when you voted for us at the shareholder's meeting.

335
00:26:55,090 --> 00:26:56,590
Do you like me that much?

336
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:59,940
Do you really think I gave you my vote because I like you?

337
00:27:01,300 --> 00:27:03,480
Do you like Hye Jeong that much?

338
00:27:04,380 --> 00:27:05,870
Yes.

339
00:27:06,950 --> 00:27:09,670
Can't you like me more then her?

340
00:27:11,610 --> 00:27:15,120
- Are you okay?
- I almost threw up.

341
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:16,400
Why are you like this to me?

342
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:20,130
What do you mean why? It's because I like you.

343
00:27:20,130 --> 00:27:22,620
Gee there are so many ways you make me give up on her.

344
00:27:22,620 --> 00:27:24,010
You can give her up if I act like this?

345
00:27:24,010 --> 00:27:26,190
Yes, I can.

346
00:27:26,190 --> 00:27:29,630
I'd give it a shot if you weren't such a strong opponent.

347
00:27:31,690 --> 00:27:34,560
How about Seo Woo? Something can't be worked out?

348
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:37,350
Seon Woo is just a kid sister to me.

349
00:27:37,350 --> 00:27:41,260
I feel like looking after her these days.

350
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:44,840
- So, I won't meddle in your business.
- What did you meddle in?

351
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:49,600
Looking for Director Jin's weaknesses... I can help you.

352
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:51,500
You don't have to. I found it.

353
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:53,490
- You did?
- Yeah.

354
00:27:53,490 --> 00:27:56,070
Then, why aren't you using it?

355
00:27:57,390 --> 00:27:58,810
Here.

356
00:28:03,930 --> 00:28:06,580
Go ahead and speak. You can say anything.

357
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:10,420
Do you know that Professor Hong is going to the research center because of me?

358
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:14,310
I know. When are you going to marry Ji Hong?

359
00:28:14,310 --> 00:28:16,510
Why don't you rescue our bachelor?

360
00:28:16,510 --> 00:28:18,040
Chief...

361
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:20,320
I'm not joking.

362
00:28:20,320 --> 00:28:23,670
I want to know what else he's not doing because of me.

363
00:28:26,750 --> 00:28:29,680
Director Jin told me that

364
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:33,000
I'm an obstacle to Professor Hong's life.

365
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:39,550
I respect you, Chief. I trust you.

366
00:28:39,550 --> 00:28:45,090
You wouldn't make me Professor Hong's obstacle, would you?

367
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:54,640
Well, I can't get away with not telling you.

368
00:29:06,650 --> 00:29:10,980
What Granny wants is for you to be happy,

369
00:29:10,980 --> 00:29:15,350
not to give up your today to find out facts surrounding her death.

370
00:29:33,170 --> 00:29:35,410
My baby...

371
00:30:17,470 --> 00:30:19,740
Have you been well, Grandma?

372
00:30:20,670 --> 00:30:23,180
I haven't been so well.

373
00:30:25,230 --> 00:30:29,160
As you know, Grandma, I know to focus on one thing at a time.

374
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:34,860
I've been obsessing over your accident all my life,

375
00:30:36,630 --> 00:30:39,270
but I'm not happy.

376
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:42,950
I'm not becoming happy.

377
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:49,900
But you know Teacher Hong, right? The one who stayed in our home.

378
00:30:51,770 --> 00:30:54,330
When I'm with him,

379
00:30:56,650 --> 00:31:01,230
I laugh and I begin to feel better.

380
00:31:08,780 --> 00:31:12,000
You like it when I'm happy, right, Grandma?

381
00:31:14,390 --> 00:31:20,230
Can I think of you only from time to time?

382
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:41,270
Sit. You said you wanted to go to work together so I made this so we can eat and then leave.

383
00:31:41,270 --> 00:31:42,620
Did you come from your house?

384
00:31:42,620 --> 00:31:45,290
I'm on my way back from visiting my grandma.

385
00:31:45,290 --> 00:31:49,110
I should go too. Let's go together next time.

386
00:31:49,110 --> 00:31:52,690
You've cheated twice. If you cheat again, you're out.

387
00:31:52,690 --> 00:31:54,970
Did I cheat?

388
00:31:54,970 --> 00:31:57,320
I met Chief Kim Tae Ho.

389
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:01,850
You froze.

390
00:32:01,850 --> 00:32:07,590
Yeah because I think you're going to chastise me. I think you chastise me often these days.

391
00:32:09,260 --> 00:32:12,310
Do what you'd like with the USB.

392
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:18,080
I know that my conversation with Director Jin was recorded. I also know that you're hesitant because of it.

393
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:22,770
I used to think if I decided and didn't act on it, I was being fake.

394
00:32:22,770 --> 00:32:24,860
But now it's different.

395
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:27,580
How can I do everything?

396
00:32:28,220 --> 00:32:30,860
You chastise Director Jin.

397
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:35,430
You have the power that I don't have.

398
00:32:36,940 --> 00:32:42,530
If you miss out on this opportunity because of me, I'm going to hate myself forever.

399
00:32:42,530 --> 00:32:46,190
He said he'd sue you for blackmail, using the voice transcript.

400
00:32:46,190 --> 00:32:53,110
Then your past will resurface and I don't know how it would harm you.

401
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:57,360
I can resolve it head on. I lived like that all this time.

402
00:32:58,510 --> 00:33:01,210
You can have that amount of faith in me.

403
00:33:11,330 --> 00:33:13,310
It looks delicious.

404
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:19,730
Finally, our long awaited project

405
00:33:19,730 --> 00:33:23,530
Guk Il Geriatric Wellness Center will begin its construction.

406
00:33:30,570 --> 00:33:36,090
As you can see in the handouts you have in front of you, Moon Jeong Construction has been selected as the contractor.

407
00:33:36,090 --> 00:33:40,410
For the construction fund, we'll spend around 120 billion won ($107 million USD).

408
00:34:02,530 --> 00:34:06,410
We finally did it! I feel like I pulled a rotten tooth out.

409
00:34:06,410 --> 00:34:09,210
Did you see Kim Tae Ho's face? As if he chewed on something bad.

410
00:34:09,210 --> 00:34:11,510
Professor Hong should've been there!

411
00:34:14,450 --> 00:34:16,460
I didn't see Yoon Do.

412
00:34:16,460 --> 00:34:20,490
He's someone who usually doesn't have any interest in this type of thing, but he just came in this one time.

413
00:34:30,590 --> 00:34:32,310
What is it?

414
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,130
Who are you?

415
00:34:34,130 --> 00:34:36,520
We're from the Seoul Central District Prosecutors Office Special Investigation Team 1.

416
00:34:36,520 --> 00:34:38,360
Why are the Seoul Central District Prosecutors Office people here?

417
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:40,580
Chief Director Jin Seong Jong?

418
00:34:40,580 --> 00:34:42,250
That's me.

419
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:45,300
Chief Director Jin Seong Jong,

420
00:34:45,300 --> 00:34:51,120
