00:34:52,430 --> 00:34:55,530
You have the right to a lawyer and the right to remain silent.

423
00:34:55,530 --> 00:34:59,580
Anything you say may be used against you at court.

424
00:34:59,580 --> 00:35:01,170
Who's the person above you?

425
00:35:01,170 --> 00:35:03,260
Will you accompany us?

426
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:06,480
If we investigate, I think you'll be linked to this.

427
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:11,590
That's not true. He isn't.

428
00:35:14,230 --> 00:35:18,420
Father! Father!

429
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:24,330
