00:36:21,350 --> 00:36:23,080
Director Jin won't stay still.

443
00:36:23,080 --> 00:36:28,670
I'm aware. The past doesn't have more power than the present so I'll get through it.

444
00:36:28,670 --> 00:36:32,300
Aish... I'm a little scared.

445
00:36:32,300 --> 00:36:34,260
You're cute.

