448
00:36:39,410 --> 00:36:41,970
I think I'd be scared if it was your issue.

449
00:36:41,970 --> 00:36:43,960
I'm not scared because it's my issue.

450
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:46,300
You're kind of cute.

