454
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:57,770
Anyway, you're so obsessive about winning and losing.

455
00:36:57,770 --> 00:37:02,150
I'm not obsessing. Aren't you driving me into that corner too much?

456
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:08,590
What is it?

457
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:09,620
I want to kiss you.

