473
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:11,090
I won't leave Hong Ji Hong alone. It was he who tipped off the prosecutor's office.

474
00:38:19,070 --> 00:38:21,380
Where did it go?

475
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:29,780
The lawyer is here.

476
00:38:30,470 --> 00:38:31,710
Does a restraining order make sense?

477
00:38:31,710 --> 00:38:33,760
I think they believe there's a reasonable fear of tampering with evidence.

478
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:35,290
They've already requested detention during the court proceedings.

479
00:38:35,290 --> 00:38:38,090
Chief Director Jin is not a victim, but is already the accused.

